text:
If you are tourist like me with coeliac ( gluten intolerance) then this place is for you, meat lovers and veggie options are also available and everything is 100% gluten free , make sure you download the Grab app so you can place a quick order and see what is available , everything made freshly. You can do it outside of the shop the order and there‚Äôs a QR -code to scan to download different app in case you want to order, and then lady is very kind and quick and makes delicious food in 15-20 minutes and she is extremely helpful and understanding, trust me it worth the waiting!   I have ordered Chicken Cheese Tortillas (see in picture) it was very delicious!
Also bare in mind that this store is collection only or home delivery , not dining in.
Really yummy gluten free food! I love the apple crumble and beef lasagne. Owner is a really nice lady too :)

To all my friend who Is always on a lookout for gluten free/vegan meal & even living a healthier lifestyle.

@gedfree_sg was found by the founder
Naomi who was suffering from
intolerance & allergy towards gluten, eggs and dairy herself.

She wanted to create something where those sufferers don‚Äôt have to sacrifice their love for food or compromising its taste.

First time ordering and so impressed. Travelling as gluten and dairy free with my vegan boyfriend it can be hard to find food to cater to both of us. We shared the tacos and quesadillas, pumpkin pie and brownies and everything was lovely. Highly recommend- great food, great service and very knowledgeable and passionate!
